      "body_md": "# Audit Assurance Node — Release Notes\n\nSuite release: **2026.1** · Product version: **1.0.4** · Channel: GA\n\n## About this release\n\n1.0.4 is a suite version-alignment release. All six AuditToolkit suite products are advanced\ntogether to a common **1.0.4** baseline so the suite ships as one coordinated release. There are no\nbreaking changes; upgrade in place via the native package.\n\nAudit Assurance Node is a technical orchestration component of the version-aligned AuditToolkit\nsuite.\n\n## What's new in 1.0.4\n\n- **Unified suite versioning.** All six suite products are aligned at 1.0.4, replacing the previous\n  mixed 1.0.2 / 1.0.3 lines.\n- **Consistent licensing and legal.** The shared End User License Agreement, Liability Disclaimer\n  and Indemnity, Copyright, and Licensing documents apply uniformly across the suite and are\n  bundled with this component.\n- **Documentation references official channels only** (official website and public release\n  channel; no private source-control hosts), verified against the signed docs manifest.\n\n## Install, upgrade and support\n\n- Installation and upgrade: see `CUSTOMER-DEPLOYMENT-PACK.md` (install/upgrade the native\n  `.deb`/`.rpm`; the package runs any required migrations on upgrade).\n- Day-2 operations and issue resolution: see the Operations and Runtime Validation documents.\n- Licensing and legal terms: see the Licensing and Legal documents in this set.\n\n## Version alignment\n\n- Suite: `2026.1` · Product (Audit Assurance Node): `1.0.4` · Channel: GA.\n- All six suite products are released together at 1.0.4.\n",
